有，但因應初中年級不需設立通識科目，故相信未來「無學校會參與、課本都唔需要再用」。<br />\n<br />\n至於《港區國安法》自6月30日通過並在港實施，當中指出須加強國家安全教育，並提高守法及安此意識。楊潤雄稱，重點是教育及認識，希望透過教育令學生培養安全意識及建立國觀念，並對國家有認同感、責任感以協助維護國家安全意識。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/5213530/org/eae4d4e1eb0ae1992b69797024315cd6.jpg/awb27YAwqCSByfe6lwxtW_BTNFS9DGaRz3yJyc98ick?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F5213530%2Forg%2Feae4d4e1eb0ae1992b69797024315cd6.jpg%2Fawb27YAwqCSByfe6lwxtW_BTNFS9DGaRz3yJyc98ick%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=e5673719&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T04:30:49.000Z","msg":"即係香港唔應該有董健華"},{"pid":"075d06f1d3177b7587aa9e986e0a99c8e47a0764","tid":2189583,"uid":174013,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T04:31:11.000Z","msg":"取消通識,改背毛語錄/習近平傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c630ec2b1160999f7fcbbe1fbe4de7782f9b5105","tid":2189583,"uid":8880,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T04:33:17.000Z","msg":"一班on9搞教改 搞到香港教育收晒皮<br />\n教人批判思考 跟住又驚人地反對佢地呢個唔道理嘅政府<br />\n香港俾班on9搞死"},{"pid":"f6091c5126524262b5733428ce94ecacddee2879","tid":2189583,"uid":37796,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"9ca72476f4c52958137c95dd875c7a04d1a07d03","tid":2189583,"uid":71335,"like":265,"dislike":0,"score":265,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T04:10:44.000Z","msg":"老老豆豆 上堂都唔聽書<br />\n根本要反你就唔關通唔通識事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T04:34:58.000Z","msg":"共黨諗法就係咁<br />\n控制思想由教育開始"},{"pid":"89b6b915388ec8b571de34cbb54393df1d580df4","tid":2189583,"uid":60451,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T04:36:52.000Z","msg":"遲啲可能到其他科<br />\n「學生對病毒認知同中央有差別」<br />\n所以取消生物科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c3c26c50f2587208e93705979e711f29ba42ad1","tid":2189583,"uid":150982,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"