加強國家安全教育，並提高守法及安此意識。楊潤雄稱，重點是教育及認識，希望透過教育令學生培養安全意識及建立國觀念，並對國家有認同感、責任感以協助維護國家安全意識。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/5213530/org/eae4d4e1eb0ae1992b69797024315cd6.jpg/awb27YAwqCSByfe6lwxtW_BTNFS9DGaRz3yJyc98ick?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F5213530%2Forg%2Feae4d4e1eb0ae1992b69797024315cd6.jpg%2Fawb27YAwqCSByfe6lwxtW_BTNFS9DGaRz3yJyc98ick%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=e5673719&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T11:32:02.000Z","msg":"Cls Dllm"},{"pid":"53627cb8cfa95c49175b323bbcb0572ac8818bcf","tid":2189583,"uid":235501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T11:32:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1637d7057d04cc2f361869c8b34e84201a031db","tid":2189583,"uid":259901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T11:34:27.000Z","msg":"通識一開頭都係你哋話推先<br />\n想點先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb129f4338ecd0c4732d9baea203fcd6e37fc87f","tid":2189583,"uid":175986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T11:34:49.000Z","msg":"On9在思想仲停留係焚書坑儒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca1964583420c8de7c87bd82be0c6243c239e79d","tid":2189583,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T11:35:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7d40a1e75963162b1ca997516272b8fcd195080c","tid":2189583,"uid":20584,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T11:40:00.000Z","msg":"當初DSE雞屌鳩你開咩通識科做必修 你就大大聲話好撚有用 教人批判思考 <br />\n<br />\n而家又話無必要"},{"pid":"925e973de558dd21782b0ace1a18d3448b29abff","tid":2189583,"uid":316463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T11:42:53.000Z","msg":"不如取消全部科目，中英數通都咪撚讀啦，<br />\n強制小朋友學習擺地攤賣嘢幫補吓國家刺激經濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gi